Figure Viewer is part of Cursed Earth spikes.
Check http://cursedearth.sourceforge.net/ for more details.

More informative README will be available later.

Try figviewer -h for help.

Some examples:
figviewer -b /path/to/evil_islands -p rick unmori
figviewer -b /path/to/evil_islands -p troll00 -a uattack unmotr
figviewer -b /path/to/evil_islands -p dragon01 -a cidle unmodg
figviewer -b /path/to/evil_islands -p dragon01 -a ubriefing01 unmodg
figviewer -b /path/to/evil_islands -p succubus00 -a cidle unmosu
figviewer -b /path/to/evil_islands -p troll00 -a uattack unmotr
figviewer -b /path/to/evil_islands -p lizardman00 -a cidle01 unmoli
figviewer -b /path/to/evil_islands -p mainmenu00 -s mainmenu00labels unmoco2
